reviewText: I have viewed this volume many times, as it was only one in library...finally decided to purchase 1&2; now I  can enjoy them any time I  want.. good decision. Quality excellent, delivery as promised. Soundtract is great!

HE MUST CHOOSE BETWEEN LOVE AND MONEY. THE ONE HE TRULY LOVES IS FROM A MIDDLE CLASS FAMILY WHILE THE ONE WHO LOVES  HIM IS RICH. CAN HE WALK AWAY FROM THE LOVE OF HIS LIFE. YOU MAY BE SURPRISED BUT  WOULD NEVER KNOW UNTIL YOU WATCH.
THESE 2 DROP DEAD GORGEOUS WOMEN AND BAE YONG JOON WILL KEEP YOU GLUED TO YOUR SEAT.  I HAVE THE WHOLE SET OF 44 EPISODES AND HAVE WATCHED IT  TWICE ALREADY.
